{"tid":2476470,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實有無人認同,好多香港人都有欺善怕惡既性格,搞到賤人同小人上晒位","createTime":"2021-04-05T13:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T02:17:10.000Z","uid":88737,"like":166,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"cdec03d0607050eaec9214869329c62acc164d32","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"其實有無人認同,好多香港人都有欺善怕惡既性格,搞到賤人同小人上晒位,先會搞到今時今日咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發現香港人好中意係揀人黎恰,例如番工遇到老細好人就會hea做,遲到早退;<br />\n<br />\n但係遇到西老細,就唔會做番同樣既野,仲要無限ot無投訴(鯰魚效應),<br />\n<br />\n久而久之班賤人/小人因為壓榨到更多勞力上晒位,而好人就會被劣幣驅逐良幣<br />\n<br />\n影響到香港好多油水位都比賤人/小人控制住,仲有樓/地,加埋政府果條大水喉,都係比小人賤人控制住,<br />\n<br />\n之後香港人就會話個個老細都係咁西嫁啦,咁去合理化呢件事,但事實上係佢地自己一手做成呢個現象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家會唔會察覺到有咁既現象? <br />\n<br />\n察覺到就比正評,唔覺就比負評<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以講下原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7316dbe6406654498180f270b0ee77829d84ec39","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":25,"dislike":8,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁講下點解西方無呢個問題呢?好重要因為西方行緊自由市場同民主制度<br />\n<br />\n上面所講既賤人同小人平日肯定得罪唔少人,係西方社會每當遇到 經濟轉型 或者 政權交替,佢地都可能會被自然淘汰甚或人為清算,<br />\n<br />\n呢班賤人同小人唔知自己幾時失勢,幾時變condom,所以佢地唔敢做得太賤怕比人尋仇或者搵夠就收山,<br />\n<br />\n咁係自由市場再上一層既老細見到呢班 賤人/小人無為佢地帶黎額外既效益;<br />\n<br />\n而且呢班人亦都有人格方面既隱憂,有機會會做出損害公司/機構既利益既事,例如偷公司/機構資料,<br />\n<br />\n咁所以就唔會特別去請/晉升呢D賤人同小人,<br />\n<br />\n咁就限制左賤人同小人向上流動既機會,就算做唔到完全既良幣驅逐劣幣都可以防止小人當道,"},{"pid":"b39480a41430ed51aaa5b4b3a88ed36ddc649551","tid":2476470,"uid":373680,"like":26,"dislike":8,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"人就係咁架啦，唔關香唔香港人事"},{"pid":"603074c44f7ac0a12f408638a5f41062b3265a33","tid":2476470,"uid":327169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"小人例如林鄭月娥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e588a07d9a783f4b6820642ca27ebbe41ff5cd","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b39480a41430ed51aaa5b4b3a88ed36ddc649551","tid":2476470,"uid":373680,"like":26,"dislike":8,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"人就係咁架啦，唔關香唔香港人事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"上面我有解釋點解西方唔會咁，<br />\n<br />\n香港個情況係主要係因為中共政權好穩固，只要班小人/賤人巴結中共就唔會怕失勢，<br />\n另一方面佢地都可以買保險轉移資產去西方/美國，出事就走佬去西方/美國"},{"pid":"52e1683ab8edb3ff102418d899c66760abd6e2ce","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"603074c44f7ac0a12f408638a5f41062b3265a33","tid":2476470,"uid":327169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"小人例如林鄭月娥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"所謂既民主派都大有人在<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d0b2ffc4a993819db8cd26dbae67094a782538","tid":2476470,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n但食花生睇人仆街好開心"},{"pid":"3c844e62f2df4977f9123a89b1baeb8270123741","tid":2476470,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52e1683ab8edb3ff102418d899c66760abd6e2ce","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"603074c44f7ac0a12f408638a5f41062b3265a33","tid":2476470,"uid":327169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"小人例如林鄭月娥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"所謂既民主派都大有人在<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63f0f30d5c107bd3aad1e55bc6ec3ecd6c6c646","tid":2476470,"uid":49197,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"由細個讀書果陣已經覺,無同理心,唔會互相幫助,反而會伸多腳落去"},{"pid":"cdc174b770793ec9f2f366d8754402c17d38bd12","tid":2476470,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"對呢D人好心淡,對社會既美好憧憬都幻滅曬,然後自己都對世界冷漠,赤子之心都冇埋"},{"pid":"a77fd0d6c06dd09f04743bd1ec1203a75e3451af","tid":2476470,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63f0f30d5c107bd3aad1e55bc6ec3ecd6c6c646","tid":2476470,"uid":49197,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"由細個讀書果陣已經覺,無同理心,唔會互相幫助,反而會伸多腳落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39449084218709a0788e5990fff1de4601d5117","tid":2476470,"uid":123591,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"係 好認同 <br />\n做好心好人就會有位比人利用拎著數"},{"pid":"217e57605a76e0cface9d6dda30c293777390958","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a63f0f30d5c107bd3aad1e55bc6ec3ecd6c6c646","tid":2476470,"uid":49197,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"由細個讀書果陣已經覺,無同理心,唔會互相幫助,反而會伸多腳落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"中晒，師兄睇黎我地同類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e60f995686a1ad418958a9de784f892f23d697","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d39449084218709a0788e5990fff1de4601d5117","tid":2476470,"uid":123591,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"係 好認同 <br />\n做好心好人就會有位比人利用拎著數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"支那人格，做好人無好報，個個只係諗住點樣踩住人向上爬"},{"pid":"0d74a6e462a994a5284e0250b2bac71d14b175d9","tid":2476470,"uid":323520,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要做得好，抵得諗就越做越多，因為老細放心交野俾你做；<br />\n做到錯漏百出，唔識做既，就un un腳勁得閒，因為無人敢俾野佢做，唔放心俾佢做<br />\n大家人工又一樣，係好唔公平，但係呢種風氣真係好難糾正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1e133242ab6c7218644c34c5db8e36a377d89e","tid":2476470,"uid":323520,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"仲有d西客，嘈呀，惡呀，膠層通常就怕左佢，話滿足佢要求，但相反態度好，又唔嘈既好客，就揸到正一正黎做，由佢地等得耐d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係睇唔過眼，好唔岩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e04af20c60c34e0928da70975b26b89f8a68140","tid":2476470,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd1e133242ab6c7218644c34c5db8e36a377d89e","tid":2476470,"uid":323520,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"仲有d西客，嘈呀，惡呀，膠層通常就怕左佢，話滿足佢要求，但相反態度好，又唔嘈既好客，就揸到正一正黎做，由佢地等得耐d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係睇唔過眼，好唔岩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"